reviewText: It's terrible they don't speak english in the movie. It really take away from the movie because you don't understand what they are saying and I spent $50.00 dollars "Oh my" what a waste.

Considering most hentai are just wet noises and bad acting,  this one actually had a pretty good story. Mystery,  murder,  family secrets. I didn't even want to fap to this since it was more story and pretty interesting
